name: Part not applicable to family burial plots Note South Kona wilderness area (contingent repeal December 31, 2006).  L 2003, c 59. Cross References Kahoolawe Island Reserve, see chapter 6K.
text: Part not applicable to family burial plots.  Nothing in this part shall apply to land altering activities related to family burial plots under section 441-5.5. [L 2005, c 128, pt of §1]
